  title: "Will AI Content Sound Like My Business?",
  meta_title: "Will AI Content Sound Like My Business? | TracPost",
  excerpt: "Generic AI writes generic content. TracPost writes from a playbook built around your business, your voice, and your market.",
  content_type: "deep_dive",
